oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Grand Theaters... Mac Wiseman
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Wiseman, Mac; Gallion, Bob, 1924-1999; Roberts, Kenny; Powell, Patti;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black on yellow) Hatch poster announcing the WWVA Jamboree a and Mac Wiseman show with Mac Wiseman, Bob Gallion, Kenny Roberts, Patti Powell, Steve Lake and the swingmasters, and Rube Schafer at the Grand theater. Poster features a metal photoplate of Mac Wiseman and Bob Gallion.
